## Recommendation & Search Logic
- **Search System**: Uses MongoDB index on text fields (`name`, `brand`, `tags`, `concernType`, `category`) with case-insensitive regex or text search.
- **Recommendations**:
  - *Similar Products*: Same category or concern.
  - *Personalized*: Based on past ordered categories and skin concerns.

